:: Reptilica stands up, and remembers a recent message from the IGL, 
and his reply that entered his brother and himself into the tourny.  
Realising that the tourny was to occur in the near-future, Reptilica 
calls his brother, informing him of the need to train. ::

:: Bloodystryke ::
